name: Cellular expression
description:
A digitally created stone, spinning within a black void, living on the blockchain. The stone is created purely using math and 3D software and is reliant upon the same for survival. 

The work subtly speak to the theme of life giving systems, as the NFT engage in a juxtaposition with the physical world. 

Furthermore, the title; 'Cellular expression' hints at the condition for human submersion in reality - whether digital or physical.
